data.description: This is the one you've been waiting for! Welcome home to carefree easy living in this ranch villa with 2 bed 2 bath, 2 car garage and over 1600 square feet of main floor living! Conveniently located close to I-280, Emeis Park, and shopping. This southern exposure home has it all.  Some of the updates include; newer roof, furnace, a/c, updated kitchen with gorgeous counters, newer appliances, Pergo Peruvian Mahogany flooring, brand new deck by Lovewell, new slider from your sun room and more! There is nothing to do but to move in and enjoy.  The basement is unfinished and offers tons of storage and unlimited possibilities to finish off too! Lawn and snow removal is included in the HOA so you can lock and up go! Davenport schools.
